a.n: The seventh wave 2016, ep 2 - 3 days in rhode island, surf project and onshore

p.k: The Seventh Wave is a new lifestyle show which follows the life of worldwide surfing in its purest form. From inspiring individuals involved in surf to new surfing technologies
p.d: The Seventh Wave is a new lifestyle show which follows the life of worldwide surfing in its purest form. From inspiring individuals involved in surf to new surfing technologies, and everything in between, Seventh Wave encapsulates true surfing culture.
